data.description: Assumable VA loan at 2.875% Discover the charm of this three-level townhome featuring a convenient 2-car garage. The first floor boasts a family room with sliding doors leading to the backyard. Ascend to the second level, where an open layout bathes the space in natural light. Enjoy luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, an upgraded kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a generously sized center island. This level also encompasses a spacious living room, a separate dining area adjacent to the kitchen with access to the deck. On the top floor, find a sprawling primary bedroom with a large walk-in closet and the upgraded bathroom which offers an oversized shower for added comfort. Two additional well-proportioned bedrooms, a second full bathroom, and a conveniently located laundry room complete the upper level. Situated outside city limits, Westview South comes with the perk of no city taxes. Residents can take advantage of community amenities, including a fitness center, yoga room, clubhouse, pool, and playgrounds. Perfectly positioned for commuters, with easy access to shopping and a quick commute to Downtown Frederick. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home - act fast before it's off the market!
